  "name": "Crucible Fuinjutsu",
  "type": "feat",
  "_id": "ByOkCPwg93PS5mcg",
  "img": "systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Clans/Kajiya.png",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>The <strong data-start=\"60\" data-end=\"75\">Kajiya Clan</strong> are not only a clan of crafters but a clan of warriors as well, managing to mix <strong data-start=\"156\" data-end=\"172\">Fire Release</strong> and <strong data-start=\"177\" data-end=\"190\">Fuinjutsu</strong> with their attacks.</p><p data-start=\"214\" data-end=\"481\">Also at <strong data-start=\"222\" data-end=\"235\">3rd level</strong>, <strong data-start=\"237\" data-end=\"260\">twice per long rest</strong>, whenever a target would make a <strong data-start=\"293\" data-end=\"309\">saving throw</strong> against a <strong data-start=\"320\" data-end=\"329\">jutsu</strong> you cast containing the <strong data-start=\"354\" data-end=\"370\">Fire Release</strong> keyword, you may weave a <strong data-start=\"396\" data-end=\"404\">seal</strong> as a part of the attack, <strong data-start=\"430\" data-end=\"478\">changing the saving throw to a Charisma Save</strong>.</p><p data-start=\"483\" data-end=\"733\">Additionally, when <strong data-start=\"502\" data-end=\"530\">producing a Forge Hammer</strong> or <strong data-start=\"534\" data-end=\"571\">equipping one from your inventory</strong>, you may spend <strong data-start=\"587\" data-end=\"599\">3 Chakra</strong> to <strong data-start=\"603\" data-end=\"624\">plant a Fire Seal</strong> on the head of the weapon, allowing you to <strong data-start=\"668\" data-end=\"730\">change any damage that Forge Hammer deals into Fire Damage</strong>.</p>",
      "chat": ""
    },
